{"tid":500031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我對香港仲未死心","createTime":"2017-12-15T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T14:34:11.000Z","uid":2699,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e7f42d3500f0524ad175bdf39ca4cd37c16ce7","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"經歷過hktv、雨傘運動、魚蛋革命，呢啲遊行運動對呢個政府都係無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n我影響唔到立法會啲乜，但至少我地唔好再坐以待斃，我地至少有野做到，無論係派傳單、貼海報、街頭宣傳、噴漆，乜野都好，改變唔到個仆街政府都嘗試下改變下香港人<br />\n<br />\n民主派爭取唔到我地要嘅野，政棍就係政棍，佢地立法會嘅所作所為我一個人真係影響唔到，但至少我地積少成多，各自肯行出屋企去做啲野，唔好再做鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩好建議可以做，聖誕假期嘅夜晚，唔係唔做野啩？"},{"pid":"ae4856c909f195b90988dc70f88b2cee369143e9","tid":500031,"uid":101022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經歷過hktv、雨傘運動、魚蛋革命，呢啲遊行運動對呢個政府都係無阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n我影響唔到立法會啲乜，但至少我地唔好再坐以待斃，我地至少有野做到，無論係派傳單、貼海報、街頭宣傳、噴漆，乜野都好，改變唔到個仆街政府都嘗試下改變下香港人<br />\n<br />\n民主派爭取唔到我地要嘅野，政棍就係政棍，佢地立法會嘅所作所為我一個人真係影響唔到，但至少我地積少成多，各自肯行出屋企去做啲野，唔好再做鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩好建議可以做，聖誕假期嘅夜晚，唔係唔做野啩？</blockquote><br />\n報佳音同屌西"},{"pid":"0c4e30bbe67c00899a6d820ffa07bba21523f6bd","tid":500031,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔想做野, 係已經唔知可以做咩"},{"pid":"eb12eb2575b312266315b17ffeed93a242e86d51","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭，立法會都要等到2020<br />\n<br />\n我諗我地可以做嘅，至少 唔好怕浪費金錢，係個屋邨派傳單、痴海報，迫啲人睇下香港係點"},{"pid":"90cb502f1e7e19bd3115d142667c75b3a34ca6ce","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"9b8e93aa72a5f7f4a1b390ffab14ff4ef327d99a","tid":500031,"uid":4942,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"好多香港人已經唔想再理<br />\n<br />\n亦都無哂有領導力既人<br />\n<br />\n有都比政府搞死哂"},{"pid":"5ca090d0cb1299b285fe0c9ff2ce65a23b83f4ea","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:12:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04b800c4c3db4f7c25579507c9f9c9519c87a2c8","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多香港人已經唔想再理<br />\n<br />\n亦都無哂有領導力既人<br />\n<br />\n有都比政府搞死哂</blockquote><br />\n你肯唔肯做野？<br />\n我相信好多野可以去做，即使唔係立法會或者公眾人物<br />\n默默肯做都可以"},{"pid":"e8cbb04d2faffebff340e68041ce423ee5523e4b","tid":500031,"uid":57678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e2750b40fcd09177cc294e512892ac863aa383b","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有影響力既都走晒<br />\n上次雨傘 同 魚蛋 搞到咁大件事 改變到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你忍心睇住佢死？<br />\n我唔忍心先想做野<br />\n唔係話大事，但至少做到野"},{"pid":"efc3487e1f0b632dff0deda4cb0ef652b3778514","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7809917c3e8d2c48193b7a43c64a53b4641655fa","tid":500031,"uid":118558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"2d7fbb5881e1082fd4b41c621df5b639f54e8966","tid":500031,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7f4b2475c9c3f446c97448d3bed305da3a7900f","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港玩完都唔好比班泛民政棍呃飯食<br />\n<br />\n下次全投民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n含撚"},{"pid":"0f6f504498a6d301c703a3dd8ee8b7f09800a4ce","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你推</blockquote><br />\n推"},{"pid":"919030f16957cbe16902ba05a25d3c760b145e62","tid":500031,"uid":88252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"先唔講種票 掌心雷<br />\n而家直接否決你參選 入左都dq<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都冇咩討論空間"},{"pid":"7c8bee0c07a275dcb8fff69b0fd5cd4db6cc4fab","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先唔講種票 掌心雷<br />\n而家直接否決你參選 入左都dq<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都冇咩討論空間</blockquote><br />\n種票掌心雷我記得當初好似有做過野<br />\n好似係門口監察，至少有做過<br />\n<br />\n立法會dq我改變唔到啲乜<br />\n咁由低做起，由淺入深咁去影響下人都得啩？"},{"pid":"fade28d49365d83e3e4adffb3381ef95ccac87ff","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ad8ecc13dbb50fec059d7e53bbc3f345d262041","tid":500031,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a4e2cc548d00ab66b20722330e554fa29481447","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搶奪輿論好緊要，不論用咩方法宣揚建制派港共政權衰野，</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n要做野<br />\n我想嘅係設計a5傳單，派同貼"},{"pid":"e0ac35ab69c29abcd61beef4579bf712b7c01b79","tid":500031,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港玩完都唔好比班泛民政棍呃飯食<br />\n<br />\n下次全投民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nag9ger"},{"pid":"9f44a8edb229e653db229fe65839536739c5bcaa","tid":500031,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"除咗同中共鬥長命諗唔到可以做咩主動嘢"},{"pid":"c12d5cc5c0224ead7bd8112abb6acca7b998ed26","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗同中共鬥長命諗唔到可以做咩主動嘢</blockquote><br />\n至少唔好好似澳門咁<br />\n用we chat，全部無主見，奶共"},{"pid":"70357cc25bb3dc7ba1696b83a4e08ff2b7476f5e","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除咗同中共鬥長命諗唔到可以做咩主動嘢</blockquote><br />\n至少唔好好似澳門咁<br />\n用we chat，全部無主見，奶共</blockquote><br />\n我唔想我嘅下一代活係地獄<br />\n<br />\n至少慢慢改變佢地嘅諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862a39f13daeabd3a687e6d2b725841ba4c82235","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe22c1b8e7ac55dd57747ea982be936bdf59883d","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531f062fa25cfb84b265767a9190937b99a223cb","tid":500031,"uid":57678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cfcfaa35d392455eef90d808bb17186a22bff54","tid":500031,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca3f85a9ab738e965c469550b5aadeade5ca3bb4","tid":500031,"uid":2699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有影響力既都走晒<br />\n上次雨傘 同 魚蛋 搞到咁大件事 改變到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你忍心睇住佢死？<br />\n我唔忍心先想做野<br />\n唔係話大事，但至少做到野</blockquote><br />\n加油牙 要返工 不了 十卜梨牙</blockquote><br />\n夜晚做都得啩？<br />\n假膠開心咩"},{"pid":"1e5efb30d5512852691754d3c60906799a9337c2","tid":500031,"uid":74775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"三子 入獄 出來帶領發聲嘅人都無"},{"pid":"c4ee01d0a812e93494df100b37a7485c5bc3c064","tid":500031,"uid"